body:
For example , when i  execute script:
`print(models.densenet121)`
 in the pytorch-master(eg: */pytorch-master) , it will output layer name normally.
but if i execute this script in a subfolder of pytorch-master(eg: */pytorch/densenet/) ,i got  error like this:
```
models.densenet121
AttributeError:creator
```
